values:
Does anyone know if there is a specialty cheese shop in Charlotte? 

i can't wait til i have my own place so i can serve gourmet dinner to all of my friends...

btw I love cookbooks. esp the Culinary Institute of America ones.

I graduate in May 06 and I've already started applying for jobs!!!!!!! It is never too early because average post graduate job search takes around 7 months in America! I am constantly busy now that school's really moving along, first exam of the semester is tomorrow and i'm here procrastinating, i have 40 pages left to read before the test.  yikes! but i can handle the pressure. i may need to take a nap after work tomorrow.  I love working at the Blumenthal Performing arts center, the people in there are so nice and i met the vice president today and her office is right next to mine.  I am learning so much each day and i'm so grateful for a chance to be part of this organization.  I better get a job out of this!
